data.description: Charming 3 bed, 2 bath manufactured home nestled in Danielsville, Georgia. Built in 1999, this cozy residence offers modern comforts in a serene setting. Enjoy spacious living areas, ideal for family gatherings or quiet evenings. The property is situated in the highly coveted zone for Ila Elementary, renowned for its excellent education standards. With its convenient location and well-maintained features, this home presents a fantastic opportunity for comfortable living. Don't miss out on the chance to make this gem yours!
